wikipedia_page.main:
Innes Senior (born 30 May 2000) is a professional rugby league footballer who plays as a winger and centre for Wakefield Trinity in the Betfred Super League, on a season long loan from the Huddersfield Giants.
He has spent time on loan from Huddersfield at Workington Town in Betfred League 1, and Wakefield in the Super League.

response: Some of that team have now made the step up to first grade level and as of 2020 Jake Wardle, Oliver Russell, Innes Senior, Louis Senior, Sam Hewitt, Jon Luke Kirby,  Dominic Young are part of the first team squad.
